{{version030}}
{{flavour|Adds malice to hellish fires, binding it with flame into a creeping inferno.}}

'''Stoke Flames''' is a monster-only spell which summons a single [[creeping inferno]]. Creeping infernos are 1 HP enemies that aren't likely to move when in [[line of sight]] and far away, but are more likely to move as they get closer. When destroyed, a creeping inferno creates a [[Fire Storm]] (8d8.25 damage).

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Stoke Flames was added in [[0.28]], along with [[stoker]]s.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
